</taxonomicName>
, which are all male have no significant morphological variation. That of 
<taxonomicName id="3C844D19E41F6E454C3DFF2AFBB3FF28" authorityName="* Cockerell" authorityYear="1921" box="[818,1029,213,235]" class="Insecta" family="Colletidae" genus="Paracolletes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="58" pageNumber="59" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="plebius">
